?"foursquare_id"=1234&device_token=1234&first_name=testy&last_name=testerson

*test POST
curl -v -H "Content-Type: application/json" -X POST -d '{"foursquare_id": "1234",
    "device_token": "1234",
    "first_name": "testy",
    "last_name": "testerson"}' \
http://localhost:3000/register

